  "detailed_description": "Take control of Flip and break every brick! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2444250/extras/dd1aea16093a9176ab7c7100850f5c5c.avif?t=1708195077\" width=376 height=81 /></span><br>Flipshot is a Breakout style game with exciting challenges and a unique aesthetic. Use Flip to break every brick on screen and complete each level.<br><br>FEATURES:<br>- Action packed brick breaking challenges 🧱⚪️<br>- Full keyboard and controller support ⌨️🎮<br>- Real life landscape footage 🎥🏞<br>- Bangin' original soundtrack 🎧📀<br>- Dynamic sound effects 🔊👂<br>- Unlockable extras! 🔓🎁",
